#UNFINISHED - PROJECT SEEMED GOOD BUT WE PIVOTED

#GrindClaw


##PROJECT Description
GrindClaw is an OpenClaw-Integrated AI Personal Assistant/Motivator. 
Having trouble sticking to your goals?
Want more accountability in your life? 
Tired of procrastinating?
GrindClaw is here to help.
GrindClaw motivates users to actually make change in their life by acting as a alarm clock, to-do list, progress tracker, and life coach by checking in multiple times a day. 

The best part? YOU are the one motivating yourself. By using a discord chat log personality scanner, GrindClaw emulates your speech patterns and vocabulary so that YOU are the one holding yourself accountable. 
